menu "ESP-NOW link"
    config RECEIVER_PEER_MAC
        string "Hardcoded peer MAC (V0)"
        default "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF"
        help
            Six-byte MAC of the transmitter, colon-separated (e.g. 84:F7:03:AA:BB:CC).
            MUST be changed before any production build.
            V0 contract: if left at the default placeholder, the firmware will log a
            warning at boot and the link will not work until a real MAC is configured.
            See docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-26-receptor-design.md §10.
endmenu
